@startuml
title GET /api/create_steam_order - Проверка возможности зачисления на DonateHub (Replenishment)
start

:Params: **account**, **amount**;

:**Config** = application config;

#palegreen :GET /api/create_steam_order\nwith query params: `account` = **account**, `amount` = **amount**;

:**Response**;
note: A3.R2

if (**Response.Code** = HTTP 200?) then (+)
    :**Response.Body**;
    stop
endif

if (**Response.Code** = HTTP 400 AND\n**Response.Body.error_message** = **Config.DonatehubErrorsMessages.AccountNotFound**?) then (+)
    :HTTP 400 BadRequest\nwith error code **Config.ErrorCodes.InvalidSteamAccount**;
    note
        Аккаунта Steam не существует.
        Введите другой
        ====
        DigitalGoods:STM_1002
    end note
    end
endif

if (**Response.Code** = HTTP 401?) then (+)
    :HTTP 401 Unauthorized;
    end
endif

:HTTP 400 BadRequest;
end

@enduml